snippet.title: Harry Styles' Vogue Cover: Behind The Scenes
snippet.description:
Harry Styles becomes the first man to get a solo Vogue cover, plus Amber Heard reacts to people wanting her out of “Aquaman” and Ellen Pompeo on how “Grey’s Anatomy” pulled off that huge surprise last night.
